Hello, thank you for calling Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Henry Coleman. How can I assist you today?

Hi Henry! I'm so excited to speak with you. My name is Elizabeth Rodriguez, and I'm calling to track the delivery of my yacht.

It's great to speak with you, Elizabeth! Can I start by confirming your delivery number, please?

Absolutely! The delivery number is three four five six seven.

Thank you, Elizabeth. Can you also provide me with the zip code of your delivery address to ensure I'm looking at the correct order?

Of course! The zip code is zero two eight four zero.

Perfect, thank you. Let me look that up for you... Alright, your yacht is scheduled for delivery in three days!

That's amazing news, Henry! I can't wait to see it.

I'm glad to hear you're as excited as we are, Elizabeth! Thank you for choosing Aquidneck Yacht Brokers.

Thank you for your time, and if you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!

Thank you, Henry! You too!
